					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13301816#post-4640051</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13301816/scp-5812#post-4640051</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sun, 10 May 2020 06:34:06 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>tgjer</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1649421</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Do I understand the correlations correctly?</p> <p>The cemetery is manifesting reverse ghost babies. It sounds like a reverse ghost baby manifests in the cemetery when someone in Glasgow gets pregnant. Or maybe these are the ghosts of the people buried in the Glasgow Necropolis, lining up for their chance at reincarnation as a baby born in the area?</p> <p>Glasgow area deaths, GRI admissions, and surgery decrease the number of ghost baby manifestations, maybe because people are less likely to have sex/get pregnant when dealing with medical emergencies? And when someone gives birth the number of manifestations drops as one of them is born.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13301816#post-4640004</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13301816/scp-5812#post-4640004</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sun, 10 May 2020 05:44:09 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>cybersqyd</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>5336470</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Do you have suggestions for making it less obtusely-formatted?</p> <p>Like, to me the table feels like a good way to convey the Foundation floundering without drawing it out too much, and I was intending to avoid like, a series of short, prose lines that'd be awkward to read. Expanding on the things more feels&#8230;unsatisfying to read because there's not the narrative depth to justify many words?</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13301816#post-4639996</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13301816/scp-5812#post-4639996</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sun, 10 May 2020 05:38:37 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>cybersqyd</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>5336470</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>At the end of the day, this was a creative decision. I figured the most interesting aspect was the base anomaly, and the most interesting way to convey that was a short, tight, slightly obtuse narrative; since there's really only like two interesting things happening here.</p> <p>That said: if you want to hit me up with more concrete suggestions, I'll totally take 'em on board?</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
